name: Multi-denominational Temple 2045
description:
This space is a multi-dimensional temple, where virtual beings can come to pray, fly, sculpt, and climb. Scribbling and doodling in virtual reality is a novel and serene experience, it’s fascinating how an abstract space can carry memories of conversations had during its construction. 

Sculpted in VR by Sky Goodman and Shawn Chiki
Textured and Rendered by Shawn Chiki
